🇸🇬SG Food: @beastandbutterflies from @msocialsingapore is offering takeaway and delivery services. Enjoy 20% off for takeaways and complimentary nostalgia old-school games is given for each takeaway.
Swipe left for the close up dishes including their signature Beast Burger & Pork Knuckle!
Orders can be made directly from the restaurant via phone call, email or their official website. #hzfooddiary #msocialsingapore #mymillennium
